config BR2_PACKAGE_XENIA_EDGE
    bool "xenia-edge"
    depends on BR2_x86_64
    select BR2_PACKAGE_PYTHON_TOML
    help
      Xenia Edge is an experimental fork of Xenia Canary with Linux and Vulkan
      enhancements, distributed here as a native Linux AppImage.

      https://github.com/has207/xenia-edge
